authorBio:
Lance Larsen (Microsoft MVP) is the Chief Visionary Officer (CVO) of HOLOSOFT as well avid community speaker, technology evangelist -and- president of MADdotNET, the Madison .NET developer community www.MADdotNET.com!

At HOLOSOFT, we've thrown ourselves into the deep end of MR/AR/VR; Mixed Reality, Augmented Reality and Virtual Reality - and we'll catch you up on what we've learned, available technologies, emerging technologies and the tools we use to write beautiful applications.

Lance is also one of the original organizers of That Conference (www.ThatConference.com) - the original Summer Camp for Geeks in the Wisconsin Dells!

